        dc:description           "Figure 25. Mangilia pertabulata Sturany, 1903, Station 145 (Dahlak Archipelago, Eritrea, Red Sea). A-D, F-G. Holotype, NHMW 84255: front (A-B), right side (C), back (D), protoconch (F), microsculpture (G). E. Original figure by Sturany (1903). Scale bars: A-D: 1 mm, F-G: 0.2 mm." ;
